<anchor n="T.50.2061.0819b25"/><head>護法篇論</head><p xml:id="pT50p0819b2501"><lb
n="0819b25" ed="T"/>論曰：九重<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1162"/>所以成深嚴，七<anchor xml:id="beg0819004" n="0819004"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>禮</sic><corr>札</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0819004"/>其能<anchor xml:id="beg0819005" n="0819005"/>捍<anchor xml:id="end0819005"/>憂<lb
n="0819b26" ed="T"/>患<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1163"/>。高墉峻壘，加校尉而守之；犀革兕皮，介<lb
n="0819b27" ed="T"/>將軍而戰者。君既安所，臣亦建功。猶<name>釋</name>門<lb
n="0819b28" ed="T"/>之外侮忽來，得法將之中權<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1167"/>斯敵，使其大道<lb
n="0819b29" ed="T"/>喪而重復，玄<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>剛</sic><corr>綱</corr></choice>絕而又張。「我有<persName key="A002891">仲由</persName>，惡言不<pb n="0819c" xml:id="T50.2061.0819c" ed="T"/><lb
n="0819c01" ed="T"/>入<ptr target="#n1870"/>」──外禦其侮，不可暫亡也。嗟乎！真教東傳，<lb
n="0819c02" ed="T"/>累更年紀，受其艱否，<anchor xml:id="beg0819006" n="0819006"/>屈<anchor xml:id="end0819006"/>指可尋！法繫有<lb
n="0819c03" ed="T"/>為，四相<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1168"/>以之遷貿；明雖無損，一輪以之蝕<lb
n="0819c04" ed="T"/>侵<ptr target="#n1871"/>。<persName key="A002824">桓楚</persName>無端効<persName key="A002757"><anchor xml:id="beg0819sgsz13"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>奔</sic><corr>莽</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0819sgsz13"/></persName>，得時而變法<ptr target="#n2279"/>；<persName key="A002043">德輿</persName>伊始<lb
n="0819c05" ed="T"/>欺孤<ptr target="#n2280"/>，餘力而責僧<ptr target="#n2281"/>。賴<persName key="A001204">遠<roleName>公</roleName></persName>之致書，因朝達<lb
n="0819c06" ed="T"/>之抗疏，只成暴政，空鯁人情。<persName key="A002596">元魏</persName>懷邪，<persName key="A004350">周<lb
n="0819c07" ed="T"/>邕</persName>尚辯，<persName key="A002289">曇始</persName>乃呈其詭迹<ptr target="#n2282"/>，<persName key="A005929">道安</persName>盛奮其辭<lb
n="0819c08" ed="T"/>鋒<ptr target="#n2283"/>。是待<placeName key="PL000000000096">秦</placeName>坑<ptr target="#n2294"/>，能逃<placeName key="PL000000000098">漢</placeName>律<ptr target="#n1872"/>，<persName key="A002289">始</persName>、<persName key="A005929">安</persName>二德，疑其住壽<ptr type="glossary" target="#g11"/><lb
n="0819c09" ed="T"/>應真<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1368"/>，出沒其形，扶危拯溺者矣！<persName key="A011681">秀</persName>也鍾其<lb
n="0819c10" ed="T"/>厄運，憤此反常，上牋<ptr target="#n2065"/>若攻壘之先登，為法<lb
n="0819c11" ed="T"/>偶犯顏<ptr type="glossary" target="#g16"/>而不死。<persName key="A001192">復禮</persName>答<persName key="A011728">權</persName>文學難詞，蔚成<lb
n="0819c12" ed="T"/>解判<ptr target="#n2284"/>。<persName key="A001194">惠立</persName>斥<persName key="A011748">呂<roleName>奉御</roleName></persName>《圖注》<ptr target="#n2172"/>，免<anchor xml:id="beg0819sgsz15"/>橫<anchor xml:id="end0819sgsz15"/>窺𨵦<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1174"/>。兩面<ptr target="#n2285"/><lb
n="0819c13" ed="T"/>俱通，<persName key="A000301">玄嶷</persName>造乎《甄正》<ptr target="#n2174"/>。一場賈勇<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1176"/>，<persName key="A011753">法明</persName>定其<lb
n="0819c14" ed="T"/>《化胡》。答<persName key="A002174">孔</persName><persName key="A002104">老</persName>於<persName key="A000519">李華</persName>，名儒懾伏<ptr target="#n1873"/>。挫是非於<lb
n="0819c15" ed="T"/><persName key="A011830">韋<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>，辯勢酋強<ptr target="#n2286"/>。<persName key="A009615">邕</persName>也掩<persName key="A008847">徐</persName>，獨記於<placeName key="PL000000014411">天台</placeName>。<persName key="A010510">儼</persName><lb
n="0819c16" ed="T"/>也令<persName key="A010395">李</persName>，成書於《復性》。其或角<persName key="A011927">史華</persName>之術，因<lb
n="0819c17" ed="T"/>躡刀梯<ptr target="#n2287"/>。諫<persName key="A004215">德宗</persName>之非，乃停沙汰<ptr target="#n2288"/>。申答而驚<lb
n="0819c18" ed="T"/>李<anchor xml:id="beg0819sgsz17"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>潡</sic><corr>㴾</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0819sgsz17"/><ptr target="#n2289"/>，作謠而占<placeName key="PL000000028928">衡山</placeName><ptr target="#n2290"/>，《破邪》之論可宗<ptr target="#n2291"/>，《鑑燈》<lb
n="0819c19" ed="T"/>之頌歸我<ptr target="#n2292"/>。</p><p>以前諸德超世卓然，式遏寇<anchor xml:id="beg0819sgsz19"/>讎<anchor xml:id="end0819sgsz19"/>，<lb
n="0819c20" ed="T"/>鬩牆禦侮<ptr target="#g1178"/>。言其薄者，則發憤忘食，殊弗防<lb
n="0819c21" ed="T"/>其反<anchor xml:id="beg0819007" n="0819007"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>汗</sic><corr>污</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0819007"/>。其如臯原縱火，蘭艾之臭同焚<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1182"/>；樹<lb
n="0819c22" ed="T"/>木摧風，鸞鴟之巢共覆者，其<anchor xml:id="beg0819sgsz21"/>唯<anchor xml:id="end0819sgsz21"/><name>會昌</name>滅虐<lb
n="0819c23" ed="T"/>我法之謂乎？從<date from-iso="+0025-08-03" key="j17304061801742" to-iso="+0220-11-25">漢</date>至<date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>，凡經數厄，鍾厄爰<lb
n="0819c24" ed="T"/>甚，莫甚<persName key="A006570">武宗</persName>焉！初有道士<persName key="A012399">趙歸真</persName>者，授<ref type="person" target="#A006570">帝</ref><lb
n="0819c25" ed="T"/>留年之術，寵遇無比。每一對揚，排毀<name>釋</name>氏，<lb
n="0819c26" ed="T"/>宜盡除之。蓋以<persName key="A012399">歸真</persName>曾於<persName key="A004383">敬宗</persName>朝出入宮<lb
n="0819c27" ed="T"/>掖<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1196"/>，勢若探湯<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1199"/>。及其禍纏暴弒<ptr target="#n2295"/>，自然事體如<lb
n="0819c28" ed="T"/>漿。<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">京邑</ref>諸僧競生誚謗，<persName key="A012399">歸真</persName>痛切心骨，何<lb
n="0819c29" ed="T"/>日忘之<ptr target="#n2296"/>？還遇<persName key="A006570">武皇</persName>，因緣狎昵，署為<persName key="A012399">兩街教
<pb n="0820a" xml:id="T50.2061.0820a" ed="T"/><lb
n="0820a01" ed="T"/>授先生</persName><ptr target="#n2297"/>。時諫官抗疏，宰臣<persName key="A009040">李德裕</persName>屢言<ptr target="#n2298"/>。<persName key="A012399">歸真</persName><lb
n="0820a02" ed="T"/>懼其動搖，奏迎<placeName key="PL000000031276">羅浮</placeName><persName key="A023384">鄧元起</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000028928">南嶽</placeName><persName key="A023385">劉玄靖</persName><lb
n="0820a03" ed="T"/>入，<ref type="person" target="#A006570">帝</ref>謂神仙坐致。由是共為<anchor xml:id="beg0820sgsz1"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>椅</sic><corr>犄</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0820sgsz1"/>角，同毀<name>釋</name><lb
n="0820a04" ed="T"/>門，意報僧譏誚之<anchor xml:id="beg0820001" n="0820001"/>讎<anchor xml:id="end0820001"/>耳！眾輕覆車，群噪驚<lb
n="0820a05" ed="T"/>蟄。<placeName key="PL000000055454">須彌</placeName><anchor xml:id="beg0820sgsz3"/>𦤞<anchor xml:id="end0820sgsz3"/><anchor xml:id="beg0820sgsz4"/><g ref="#Z1178"/><anchor xml:id="end0820sgsz4"/><ptr type="glossary" target="#g1024"/>，困其劫盡之風；<name>有頂</name><ptr type="glossary" target="#g1203"/>低摧，倚<lb
n="0820a06" ed="T"/>其宿<anchor xml:id="beg0820sgsz6"/>舂<anchor xml:id="end0820sgsz6"/>之杵。詎云終否，當有復時<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1205"/>。<date notBefore-iso="+0847-02-10" key="j20304612035056" notAfter-iso="+0859-09-10"><name>大中</name></date>行<lb
n="0820a07" ed="T"/>廢教之誅<ptr target="#n2293"/>，<date notBefore-iso="+0841-02-08" key="j20282682030170" notAfter-iso="+0846-04-25"><name>會昌</name></date>非後天之老<ptr target="#n2299"/>。吁咄哉！<persName key="A012399">歸真</persName>奇<lb
n="0820a08" ed="T"/>祕之術，今古所無。何邪？能寄喜怒於天子之<lb
n="0820a09" ed="T"/>心，雖<persName key="A011267">王晉</persName>、<persName key="A007264">安期</persName>，俱弗如也。爾時<persName key="A009180">玄暢</persName>──<persName key="A009180">法寶<lb
n="0820a10" ed="T"/>大師</persName>也──納兩街之請，操一割之刀，纂輯古<lb
n="0820a11" ed="T"/>今，搜揚<ptr type="glossary" target="#g859"/>經史，成其別錄<ptr target="#n1874"/>，上其表牋。逆龍<lb
n="0820a12" ed="T"/>鱗<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1002"/>之手已伸，探虎穴之心且勇。膏<anchor xml:id="beg0820sgsz8"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>盲</sic><corr>肓</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0820sgsz8"/>之疾，<lb
n="0820a13" ed="T"/>圭刀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1207"/>之散何施？混濁之河，銖兩之膠謾<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1210"/>解。如<lb
n="0820a14" ed="T"/>皆畏震，所謂坐看<persName key="A009180">暢<roleName>公</roleName></persName>手拓<placeName key="PL000000058348">不周山</placeName>，不免<lb
n="0820a15" ed="T"/><persName key="A023386">共工</persName>之觸折也。凡今緇伍，無縱毀譏。毀譏，<lb
n="0820a16" ed="T"/>小人也。及罹禍毒，君子受之，亦猶城門火<lb
n="0820a17" ed="T"/>而池魚死也<ptr target="#n1875"/>。儻云<persName key="A004350">周武</persName>不落於<placeName key="PL000000055500">阿鼻</placeName><ptr target="#n1876"/>，<persName key="A012399">歸真</persName><lb
n="0820a18" ed="T"/>自登於仙籍，<persName key="A003667">宣宗</persName>誅<ref type="person" target="#A012399">之</ref>，已塞責矣。是故比<lb
n="0820a19" ed="T"/>丘但自觀身行，莫伺<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1211"/>玄門，非干<anchor xml:id="beg0820sgsz10"/>己<anchor xml:id="end0820sgsz10"/>事。又<lb
n="0820a20" ed="T"/>以空門染習如然，無鬪四支而傷具體，各<lb
n="0820a21" ed="T"/>是聖人設教，無相奪倫。如此行時，名真護<lb
n="0820a22" ed="T"/>法也。<persName key="A002104">老<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>云：「六親不和，則有孝子。<ptr target="#n1877"/>」如無孝<lb
n="0820a23" ed="T"/>子之名，信六親大和也。已上諸公，皆家中有<lb
n="0820a24" ed="T"/>競，號咷諫乎！因得善父母之名歟？今我傳<lb
n="0820a25" ed="T"/>家，止勸將來二教和同，弗望後生學其訐<lb
n="0820a26" ed="T"/>直<ptr type="glossary" target="#g895"/>，險在其中矣，為君不取。然則臨機可<lb
n="0820a27" ed="T"/>用，相事當行，必任弛張，勿為膠柱<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1224"/>。然後<lb
n="0820a28" ed="T"/>知時名為大法師也。《傳》又云乎：「相時而動，<lb
n="0820a29" ed="T"/>無累後人」<ptr target="#n1878"/>，其斯之謂歟！</p>
